{"id": "art-400", "label": "Art. 400", "title": "Art. 400: Minuta", "slug": "art-400", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 400: Minuta </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_104643933\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1716\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_104643933\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)În afara cazurilor în care sunt aplicabile\ndispozi&#355;iile art. 406 alin. (1), rezultatul deliber&#259;rii\ninstan&#355;ei sau, dup&#259; caz, judec&#259;torului, indiferent de\nfunc&#355;ia judiciar&#259; pe care o exercit&#259;, se consemneaz&#259; într-o\nminut&#259;, care trebuie s&#259; aib&#259; con&#355;inutul prev&#259;zut\npentru dispozitivul hot&#259;rârii.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1612458566\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1715\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1612458566\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Minuta se semneaz&#259; de membrii completului de\njudecat&#259;.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(3)Minuta se întocme&#351;te în\ndou&#259; exemplare originale, dintre care unul se ata&#351;eaz&#259; la\ndosarul cauzei, iar cel&#259;lalt se depune, spre conservare, la dosarul de\nminute al instan&#355;ei.</span></p>"}